==[#13] [#Aur] Current version Package Build for Arch Linux ==

- [gtk-theme-onestepback.zip gtk-theme-onestepback.zip]
- [gtk-theme-onestepback-darker.zip gtk-theme-onestepback-darker.zip]

Use of the Aur Package :

```
unzip gtk-theme-onestepback.zip
cd gtk-theme-onestepback
makepkg -s
pacman -U gtk-theme-onestepback-0.995-1-any.pkg.tar.zst
```

